comments: Adebayo (MIA) briefly engages with Holiday (IND) as they separate after the pick.
Adebayo (MIA) and Turner (IND) briefly engage and separate during the rebound.
Oladipo (IND) makes marginal contact with Adebayo (MIA).
Butler (MIA) switches his pivot foot after receiving the pass.
Warren (IND) makes marginal contact with Butler (MIA).
Adebayo (MIA) sets the screen on Warren (IND) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Warren (IND) makes contact with Adebayo's (MIA) arm and affects his shot attempt.
Dragic (MIA) maintains a legal guarding position on Brogdon (IND) during the drive.
Butler (MIA) cleanly blocks the shot attempt by Warren (IND).
Holiday (IND) maintains a legal guarding position on Butler (MIA) at the end of the drive.
Turner (IND) makes marginal contact with Dragic (MIA) on the close out.
Correctly called 24 second violation.
Dragic (MIA) maintains a legal guarding position on Warren (IND) during the drive and makes contact with the ball.
Oladipo (IND) makes contact with Butler (MIA) that affects his SQBR.
Dragic (MIA) makes contact with Brogdon (IND) that affects his SQBR.
Adebayo (MIA) does not get up to ball height and makes contact with Holiday's (IND) wrist after he releases the shot attempt and affects his follow-through.
Holiday (IND) commits a take foul on Butler (MIA).
Warren (IND) takes more than two steps after he has gathered the ball.
Turner (IND) commits a take foul on Dragic (MIA).
Dragic (MIA) is in an established position in Holiday's (IND) path and absorbs the contact initiated by Holiday during the jump shot attempt
Holiday (IND) commits a take foul on Crowder (MIA). Due to a clock/ table error this foul occurs at :05.4.
